â€œWow...

Had three pulls on this from my water bong and it turned this seasoned vet into a noob fast.
I can get prone to anxiety when smoking some sativa heavy strains but thought I mostly learned to handle the controls. Boy was I wrong.
Simultaneously sunk into the couch and experienced a big head buzz. Hax a great time but made me mildly paranoid and awake during bedtime.
Treat this one with respect.â€

â€œYou can tell Curaleaf puts a lot of care into this strain. The buds are perfect, hardly any stem. There are no little seeds or seed casings- just frosty, visibly SPARKLING nugget. The smell is an adventure, it's incredibly pungent and fruity cherry at the same time. As soon as I opened the bottle...â€

â€œA beautiful strain to the eye.  Leaves tended to be on the darker side.  Wonderful earthy smell with overtones of pine and cherry.  Bold, citrus taste.
